The following line to be added to the end of the autostart file

@sudo /usr/share/radio/gradio.py

There are two versions of the autostart file
For Bullseye or earlier 
the autostart file is ~/.config/lxsession/LXDE-pi/autostart

For Bookworm or later 
the autostart file is ~/.config/lxsession/LXDE/autostart

This starts the graphical version of the radio 
See example autostart files in this directory

LXDE.autostart      Bookworm or later
LXDE-pi.autostart   Bullseye or earlier
